The Idea of ETOR coin started in Q1 2018 to implement South Asia’s Biggest Exchange.

To develop Crypto Games, Etor Exchange, Shopping Portal, Travel Portal, Crypto Banks.

ETHROI is supported with business model where the raised funds are utilized for opening up for new exchanges, also for Crypto Hedging, Forex Hedging, Forex Arbitrage , Correlation Trading between crypto & forex.
